Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\b1}我 的 父 亲 母 亲\N{\fs14}本片改编自鲍十所著小说“纪念”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲突然去世了\N{\rEng}My father died suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是昨天晚上知道的\N{\rEng}I only found out last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长给我打了一个长途电话\N{\rEng}The mayor called to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时我真不敢相信\N{\rEng}I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的家在山区  一个不大的村子\N{\rEng}My hometown is in the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫三合屯\N{\rEng}a village called Sanhetun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很早就离开家乡出来工作了\N{\rEng}I left to work in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为忙  几年都回不了一次家\N{\rEng}I'm so busy I haven't been home in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是村里的小学老师\N{\rEng}My father was the village schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在当地教了一辈子书\N{\rEng}He taught there all his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是父母唯一的孩子\N{\rEng}I am an only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是村里唯一念过大学的\N{\rEng}The only one from our village who went to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在最担心的就是母亲  怕她一下子受不了\N{\rEng}I am very worried about my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师傅  进屋喝口水歇会儿吧\N{\rEng}Come in and rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了  我还要赶紧回去呢\N{\rEng}I've got to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那回去跟你们老总说  回头我当面谢他\N{\rEng}Thank your boss again for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不客气    - 谢谢啊\N{\rEng}- Thank you.    - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\rEng}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\rEng}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生子\N{\rEng}Yusheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长  夏大叔\N{\rEng}Mayor, Uncle Xia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外头看见车  才知道你回来了\N{\rEng}I saw the car and knew you were back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那进屋吧\N{\rEng}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屋里暖和\N{\rEng}It's warmer inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也坐  坐吧\N{\rEng}Please. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你去个电话  说情况也没说清楚\N{\rEng}I couldn't tell you much over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次你回来呀  给你说一说\N{\rEng}Now you're here, I can explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱村里这个学校啊\N{\rEng}It's the schoolhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸是早就要求要翻盖  多少年了吧\N{\rEng}For many years your father has wanted to rebuild it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为村里困难  也没答应\N{\rEng}but there were always reasons we couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你爸又张罗要翻盖学校\N{\rEng}He brought it up again recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里这回就决定要翻盖学校\N{\rEng}and the village agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是木料都预备够了  还缺钱\N{\rEng}We have the materials we need but not enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没钱他就急了\N{\rEng}Your father's mind was set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他着急啊  他就赶着出去借\N{\rEng}He was determined to find the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于你爸借钱  可跑了多少趟\N{\rEng}He began traveling around, trying to borrow the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿  那儿  凡是他不错的\N{\rEng}He went all over the county.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有词儿的人\N{\rEng}If he thought there was a chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他都张罗去借去\N{\rEng}he'd go after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果呢  这趟回来\N{\rEng}On the last trip, on his way home...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在路中就给赶上了风雪  特别大\N{\rEng}he ran into a snowstorm, a big blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就给激了  激病了\N{\rEng}He was stuck in the storm, and he got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两天白毛风\N{\rEng}He was too sick to be moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激病了\N{\rEng}That made him more anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激病了回来一看不行了\N{\rEng}He was in bad shape when he got back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就送到县城医院经过了看\N{\rEng}so we took him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一看啊  是心脏病\N{\rEng}They examined him, said he had a heart problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们你说老哥在这儿多少年\N{\rEng}We've known your dad all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他有心脏病  结果呢  是心脏病\N{\rEng}Who knew he had a heart condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治疗了  看了不行\N{\rEng}They tried treating him, but it was no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就结果呢  你爸也就不顶了\N{\rEng}He fought, but he didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸在哪儿呢\N{\rEng}Where is my father now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在在县医院呢  在太平房\N{\rEng}At the provincial hospital, in the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不就等着你回来\N{\rEng}That's why we wanted you to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你商量\N{\rEng}To tell you all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次通电话的时候还挺好  咋整的呢\N{\rEng}Last time I spoke with him, he seemed fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是年纪大了  再赶上风雪\N{\rEng}It was a bad storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人上岁数  再赶上这大雪天  大白毛风\N{\rEng}At his age, it was too much for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一激  受不了啦\N{\rEng}It would have been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人是不顶了\N{\rEng}hard on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们村的意思呢  是打算明天待一天\N{\rEng}The village wants to arrange a car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后天咱们用车给他接回来\N{\rEng}to bring your father back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 已经三天了    - 在咱们村给他安葬就得了\N{\rEng}- It's been three days.    - Bring him back here to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概就这个意思\N{\rEng}That's what we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就按村长的意思办吧  我没啥意见\N{\rEng}That's fine. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没啥意见  还有一个问题\N{\rEng}But there is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这问题就是你妈不同意拿车拉\N{\rEng}Your mother doesn't want to use a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要求是抬回来\N{\rEng}She wants your father to be carried back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬是啥意思啊\N{\rEng}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬就是  按老迷信说就是  再返回来走走老路\N{\rEng}She wants the coffin brought back on foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来看看这个老路  就是别忘这个老路吧\N{\rEng}so your father won't forget his way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是老一套迷信    - 那我妈是这么想的吗\N{\rEng}- It's an old tradition, a superstition.    - I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还想陪着也走回来跟着\N{\rEng}And she wants to walk with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就抬\N{\rEng}So let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬呢  咱们村里也同意\N{\rEng}We want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这教了多少年学了  要说抬  也没问题\N{\rEng}He was our village teacher. Everyone respects him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上咱们村子里  现在是年轻人都走光了\N{\rEng}But our young people have all left for the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在外面做活\N{\rEng}They've gone away to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽剩些老的老小的小\N{\rEng}Only old people and children are left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里的意思是想用拖拉机\N{\rEng}We thought of using a tractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半天也就拉回来了\N{\rEng}We could make the trip in half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这回让你回来做做你妈的工作\N{\rEng}You must help your mother decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  大爷  你们别为难\N{\rEng}I appreciate your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事儿我跟我妈说说  劝劝她\N{\rEng}I will talk it over with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对    - 唉  我妈呢\N{\rEng}- Good.    - Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸死了她就上那学校坐着\N{\rEng}Probably at the schoolhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一到学校就发呆坐着  谁劝也不行\N{\rEng}She's there every day since he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁劝也不回来    - 她这一坐就是半天\N{\rEng}- She won't listen to anyone.    - She just sits there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没啥事儿吧    - 没啥事儿\N{\rEng}- Is she okay?    - I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就怕她也\N{\rEng}I am only afraid--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是以前那学校啊\N{\rEng}The old schoolhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是以前的学校\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我过去看看\N{\rEng}I'll go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 妈    - 生儿\N{\rEng}- Mother.    - Yusheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天这么冷  咱们回家去吧\N{\rEng}It's so cold. Let's go home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸不在了\N{\rEng}Your father is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走  咱们回家  妈\N{\rEng}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也看不着你爸了\N{\rEng}You will never see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈  上炕暖和暖和吧\N{\rEng}Get on the bed where it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生子  你跟我搬织布机去\N{\rEng}Yusheng. Bring me my loom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,织布机  搬它干啥  妈\N{\rEng}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要织布\N{\rEng}I want to weave something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,织啥布\N{\rEng}Weave what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你爸织块挡棺布\N{\rEng}A cloth for your father's coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈  你看这样行不行\N{\rEng}Don't trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们别织了  我上供销社给你买一块\N{\rEng}Why don't we go buy one instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买的我不要\N{\rEng}I don't want to buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,织布机都几十年了\N{\rEng}That loom is so old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早都坏了  再说现在谁还自己织布呢\N{\rEng}It's been broken for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏了  叫你夏大叔修修嘛\N{\rEng}Why can't we fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看  妈\N{\rEng}You need rest, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两天你这身体也是太累了\N{\rEng}You must be so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也得亲手给他织一块挡棺\N{\rEng}I have to make this cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就给您买去  行吗\N{\rEng}Can't I just buy one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买的我不要  我叫你搬你就搬\N{\rEng}No, just bring me the loom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们村子里  根本就没有织布机了\N{\rEng}The only loom left in the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈呀  还留这么一个\N{\rEng}his this one of your mother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当宝贝似的留着\N{\rEng}She's guarded it like a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来呀  你妈要织布  修的这个织布机要织布\N{\rEng}Looks like she's determined to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是要抬了\N{\rEng}Just like the funeral procession.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬的意思也就是过去那么个老习惯\N{\rEng}Carrying the dead is an old custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么过个山了\N{\rEng}Over the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过个沟了  过个路口了\N{\rEng}across the river, past the crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就喊着点\N{\rEng}And we shout at him along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就喊点什么呢  什么意思呢\N{\rEng}What do we say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是走这儿  叫他记住这个道儿\N{\rEng}We tell him this is the road home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大伙在这喊着点\N{\rEng}Everyone yells at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他记住这个道儿\N{\rEng}so that he remembers his way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么个意思\N{\rEng}It's an old tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏大叔  我想问问\N{\rEng}Is it really so difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是非抬不可的话  咱村里确实有困难  真抬不了\N{\rEng}to do as my mother wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们村里确实有困难\N{\rEng}It is a problem, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个没有劳力\N{\rEng}We don't have the manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳力都出去了  加了就是老的老小的小了\N{\rEng}All our young people have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬回来  那都是文化大革命以前的事儿了\N{\rEng}No one has followed this custom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在谁抬你  确实在没有人\N{\rEng}since the Cultural Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真不想让母亲织这块布\N{\rEng}I don't want her to work like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我不知道怎样劝她\N{\rEng}but I don't know how to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把父亲抬回来\N{\rEng}The funeral procession...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是母亲现在唯一的想法\N{\rEng}seems all that matters to her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈  听老村长说  您想把爸抬回来\N{\rEng}Mother, I know about your wishes for the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想  挺麻烦的  要不然就再想个办法\N{\rEng}Is there some other way to arrange it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别替他们操心麻烦\N{\rEng}I know it won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看你爸到这村四十多年\N{\rEng}But your father lived here for 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为这个学校  给他们培养出多少左一代右一代的学生\N{\rEng}He taught many generations of kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起早睡晚的  心都操碎了\N{\rEng}He worked very hard. Long, long hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们就这么点事儿  他们给咱们讲出这么些困难\N{\rEng}The town should give him something back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那村长倒是没有别的意思\N{\rEng}The mayor agrees with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就说了个困难\N{\rEng}How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得吧  妈  你说拿人抬回来\N{\rEng}We can walk alongside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和拖拉机拉回来  不是都一样吗\N{\rEng}with the coffin pulled by a tractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不都是接我爸回来\N{\rEng}We'd still be with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个就不一样\N{\rEng}It's not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么也得找人去\N{\rEng}I want your father carried back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你爸一块儿接回来\N{\rEng}by the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不成  他们有困难  咱们想办法\N{\rEng}If they won't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们去人  一块儿把你爸接回来\N{\rEng}we'll get someone who will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天晚上就别织了  行吗\N{\rEng}Please don't work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这块布  我非得一定要把它织完了\N{\rEng}I have to. I have to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你累好几天了  你休息休息吧  行吗\N{\rEng}You are tired. Get some rest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上你爸上课那屋睡觉吧\N{\rEng}You sleep in your father's study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天还非得把它织出来\N{\rEng}I have to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片  还是父亲和母亲结婚那年照的\N{\rEng}This picture was taken the year my parents married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲原本不是我们三合屯的人\N{\rEng}My father was not from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是后来才来的\N{\rEng}He came here to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当年父亲和母亲谈恋爱的事儿\N{\rEng}The story of my parents' courtship...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经轰动一时\N{\rEng}is well-known in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里人说来说去的  听起来都像个故事\N{\rEng}Practically everyone here has heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那年母亲刚满十八岁\N{\rEng}My mother had just turned 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲也只有二十岁\N{\rEng}My father was 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听母亲说\N{\rEng}My mother told me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一辆马车把父亲拉到了三合屯\N{\rEng}my father arrived by horse cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾\N{\rEng}Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾\N{\rEng}Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是来咱们三合屯教书的先生\N{\rEng}This is our new teacher, Mr. Luo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 姓骆  叫骆长余    - 别叫先生  叫老师就行了\N{\rEng}- His name is Luo, Luo Changyu.    - Just call me Luo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是娣儿呀\N{\rEng}Is that Di?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慌慌张张的干啥呢\N{\rEng}What's all the racket for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没干啥\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今儿一大早闹闹轰轰的  都说是去看先生  先生来了吗\N{\rEng}Has the teacher arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这多好  咱们三合屯  总算也有了先生了\N{\rEng}It's about time we got our own teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那先生是啥样啊\N{\rEng}What does he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个小伙子\N{\rEng}He's a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子  小伙子就当先生了\N{\rEng}A young teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小伙子倒真能耐\N{\rEng}He must be talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他住哪儿呀\N{\rEng}Where is he staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村政府吧\N{\rEng}At the village council office.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村政府倒也行\N{\rEng}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那东屋有铺炕  吃饭呢\N{\rEng}Where will he eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃派饭  一家一天轮着吃\N{\rEng}He'll eat with a different family each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也该派到咱家\N{\rEng}When it's our turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候啊  可得给先生吃饱喽\N{\rEng}we'll have to make a good meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娣儿  你在干啥呢\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没干啥\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看先生就看先生\N{\rEng}Seeing a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还换什么新衣裳\N{\rEng}has you changing clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥的眼睛那时候已经瞎了\N{\rEng}My grandmother was already blind by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听母亲说  是姥爷死的时候\N{\rEng}Mother says when Grandfather died...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥天天哭  把眼睛给哭坏了\N{\rEng}Grandmother cried until she went blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姥爷死后\N{\rEng}After Grandfather died,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家里就没有其他人了  就母亲陪着姥姥\N{\rEng}there was only Mother to look after Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥一门心思\N{\rEng}Grandmother's only wish
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想给母亲找个好婆家\N{\rEng}was to find a good husband for Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亲的人倒是很多\N{\rEng}She had many proposals...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲一个都没看上\N{\rEng}but my mother didn't like any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲已经来了\N{\rEng}The schoolhouse was not yet built
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里的学校还没有盖好\N{\rEng}when my father arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那几天  村长正领着乡亲们赶着盖\N{\rEng}The mayor enlisted all the men's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我们当地的习俗\N{\rEng}According to our village custom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新房盖好的时候\N{\rEng}a red cloth must be hung in a new building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都要在梁上裹一块红布  图个吉利\N{\rEng}It's hung on the ceiling beam for good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这块布就叫红\N{\rEng}The cloth is called the lucky red banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常是由\N{\rEng}It must be woven
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里最漂亮的姑娘来织\N{\rEng}by the village's most beautiful maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次织红的事儿  自然又落在了我母亲的身上\N{\rEng}This task, of course, fell to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为心里有了父亲的原因吧\N{\rEng}Perhaps she was already a little in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这块红  母亲织得格外仔细\N{\rEng}because the cloth she made was especially fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当年村里有两口井\N{\rEng}The village had two wells back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前的井叫前井\N{\rEng}The old well was called the "front well."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来新打的那口井叫后井\N{\rEng}The newer well was called the "back well."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后井近\N{\rEng}The new well was nearer the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们通常都在后井打水\N{\rEng}so more people used that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从父亲来了以后\N{\rEng}After my father arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲就改在前井打水了\N{\rEng}Mother started to use the old well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样会路过学校\N{\rEng}She had to pass the schoolhouse to get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照那时候的规矩\N{\rEng}The village had another custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凡是盖房这类大事儿\N{\rEng}When putting up a new building,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家家户户都要往工地上送饭  给干活儿的男人吃\N{\rEng}each family prepared a dish for the workers' lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这叫送公饭\N{\rEng}Everyone contributed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那几天  母亲尽挑好吃的做\N{\rEng}Mother prepared all her best dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她总希望父亲能吃上她亲手做的饭\N{\rEng}hoping Father would eat what she made.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.79,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听母亲说  以前有挺多事儿  女人都不能上前\N{\rEng}Back then when something was built...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比方说盖房子  还有打井这种大事儿\N{\rEng}women were not allowed to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说怕沾上邪气儿\N{\rEng}Superstition said they would bring bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在盖学校\N{\rEng}When they put up the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里的妇女们就只能离得远远的\N{\rEng}the village women could only watch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一边看\N{\rEng}from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姐  今天你送的什么饭呀\N{\rEng}What did you make today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馒头和烙饼\N{\rEng}Steamed bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招娣  你送的什么饭\N{\rEng}What about you, Di?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送葱油饼\N{\rEng}I made onion cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你送葱油饼  我送苞米碴干饭\N{\rEng}I brought rice steamed in lotus leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苞米碴干饭可没有葱油饼好吃\N{\rEng}Onion cakes are better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留什么好吃的  晚上偷着给你男人吃呢\N{\rEng}Did you save some for your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说\N{\rEng}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没看见吗\N{\rEng}Look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是乱吃\N{\rEng}They just pick up the first dish they see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不知道谁吃的谁家的\N{\rEng}They don't know who made what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送的包子不知道谁吃了\N{\rEng}I don't know who's eating mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你男人吃了\N{\rEng}Must be your husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放着吧\N{\rEng}Put them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招娣  你把红给送来了\N{\rEng}You're already done with the banner?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还正要到你家去取呢\N{\rEng}I was going to come get it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我  给我啊\N{\rEng}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  行  给你\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还省得我给你去送呢\N{\rEng}You'll save me a further trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招娣  你这红织得可真好\N{\rEng}This is a beautiful banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过两天一上梁  学校盖好了  就能上课了\N{\rEng}The school is almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生说  第一天上语文\N{\rEng}Chinese study will be the first lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那先生这两天吃得好不好\N{\rEng}Is the teacher happy with the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.95,0:22:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也跟着吃公饭\N{\rEng}Does he eat what we make?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他也抢着吃\N{\rEng}He eats together with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪能呐  人家是城里来的文化人\N{\rEng}No. He's a city gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能和咱们一块抢着吃\N{\rEng}It's not proper for him to eat with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他咋吃的\N{\rEng}So how does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是紧着先生端头一份儿\N{\rEng}We give him first pick of the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.05,0:24:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生在世  念\N{\rEng}"In life--" Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生在世\N{\rEng}"In life--"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.56,0:24:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要有志气  念\N{\rEng}"You must make goals."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要有志气\N{\rEng}"You must make goals."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.66,0:24:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  咱们再读第二遍\N{\rEng}Start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读书识字  多长见识  念\N{\rEng}"One must learn to write." Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.07,0:24:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,读书识字  多长见识\N{\rEng}"One must learn to write."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.07,0:24:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能写会算  是件好事  念\N{\rEng}"One must learn arithmetic."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.58,0:24:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能写会算  是件好事\N{\rEng}"One must learn arithmetic."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.58,0:24:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事小情  提笔就记  念\N{\rEng}"Keep a journal faithfully."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.08,0:24:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事小情  提笔就记\N{\rEng}"Keep a journal faithfully."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.59,0:24:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知今知古  知天知地  念\N{\rEng}"Know the present, know the past."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.59,0:24:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知今知古  知天知地\N{\rEng}"Know the present, know the past."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.10,0:24:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候听母亲说起过\N{\rEng}When I was young, my mother told me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.60,0:25:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲念书的声音特别好听\N{\rEng}my father had a beautiful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.60,0:25:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲不识字\N{\rEng}My mother never learned to write,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.10,0:25:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的课文她也听不懂\N{\rEng}was never interested in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.61,0:25:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她觉得父亲的声音是天底下最好听的声音\N{\rEng}But she couldn't resist the sound of my father's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.11,0:25:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这一天开始  母亲就天天去听\N{\rEng}She went by the school every day after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.11,0:25:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来村里人习惯了  就没人再去听了\N{\rEng}For most, the novelty of the new school wore off after a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是母亲还是去听\N{\rEng}but not for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.62,0:25:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一听就听了四十多年\N{\rEng}For 40 years, she came to listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.62,0:25:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这已经成了她生活中的一部分\N{\rEng}and it became part of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.63,0:25:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长幼尊卑  敬重有序  念\N{\rEng}"Know respect for your elders."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.13,0:25:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长幼尊卑  敬重有序\N{\rEng}"Know respect for your elders."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.65,0:25:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲听说每天放学的时候\N{\rEng}Each day after school...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.15,0:25:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲都要送几个路远的孩子回家\N{\rEng}my father walked some of his students home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.16,0:26:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就动了心思  想在那条路上碰见父亲\N{\rEng}Knowing this, my mother waited along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.19,0:26:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太阳光  金亮亮  雄鸡唱三唱\N{\rEng}♪ The birds sing with the beautiful sun ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.70,0:26:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花儿醒来了  鸟儿忙梳妆\N{\rEng}♪ Their songs wake the beautiful flowers ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.65,0:31:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.67,0:31:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是谁呀\N{\rEng}Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.17,0:31:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是老田家的招娣\N{\rEng}That's Zhao Di.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.68,0:31:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那她是咱三合屯的人吗\N{\rEng}Is she from Sanhetun?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.68,0:31:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在后街那儿\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.68,0:31:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招娣姐  我们老师问你呢\N{\rEng}Di, the teacher is asking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.79,0:33:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  挑水去\N{\rEng}You need water?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.29,0:33:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.29,0:33:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来来来  我帮你挑\N{\rEng}Let me get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.31,0:33:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我自己来\N{\rEng}No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.30,0:33:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来我来\N{\rEng}Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.30,0:33:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  不  没事儿  没事儿\N{\rEng}I can do it. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.80,0:33:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你客气什么嘛  这活儿我们都干惯了\N{\rEng}No, let me. Let me help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.80,0:33:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是教书的  您怎么能干这活呢\N{\rEng}You're the teacher. You shouldn't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.81,0:34:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来  我来\N{\rEng}Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.31,0:34:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我自己来就行\N{\rEng}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.31,0:34:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.48,0:34:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我行\N{\rEng}Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.10,0:34:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招娣  你咋跑前井打水来啦\N{\rEng}Di, you're fetching water as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.34,0:34:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天该轮到我家吃饭了\N{\rEng}Tomorrow it's our turn to have you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.34,0:34:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.92,0:35:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲对我说过\N{\rEng}My father told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.92,0:36:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他第一次到母亲家吃派饭的时候\N{\rEng}the first time he went to my mother's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.93,0:36:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲站在门口迎他\N{\rEng}she stood in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.93,0:36:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他记得母亲扶着门框  站在门口的样子\N{\rEng}Leaning against the door frame...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.93,0:36:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像一幅画\N{\rEng}she looked like a figure in a painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.44,0:36:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说很多年他都忘不了这幅画\N{\rEng}an image he would never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.95,0:36:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娣儿  是先生来了吧\N{\rEng}Is the teacher here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.95,0:36:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.95,0:36:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就说嘛  这脚步声这么重\N{\rEng}Your heavy footsteps gave you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.95,0:36:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快到屋里来  我看看\N{\rEng}Come in. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.96,0:36:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我娘的眼睛坏了\N{\rEng}My mother's eyesight is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.46,0:36:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.96,0:36:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这先生这么高啊\N{\rEng}This teacher is very tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.48,0:36:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下  坐下\N{\rEng}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.00,0:36:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上炕吧\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.01,0:37:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家里多少年没有男人吃饭了\N{\rEng}Can't think when we last had a man home for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.51,0:37:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听听  吃得真香啊\N{\rEng}The food must taste good to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.02,0:37:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚼得多有劲啊\N{\rEng}You sound like you're enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.02,0:37:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生来咱们三合屯有一个月了吧\N{\rEng}How long have you been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.02,0:37:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个多月了\N{\rEng}About a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.03,0:37:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还待得惯吗\N{\rEng}Have you gotten used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.53,0:37:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待得惯\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.03,0:37:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待得惯就好\N{\rEng}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.03,0:37:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生家在县上住\N{\rEng}You're from the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.03,0:37:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,县上东关\N{\rEng}Yes, from East Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.03,0:37:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那咋来三合屯呢\N{\rEng}How did you choose Sanhetun?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.04,0:37:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校毕业  在家没事儿\N{\rEng}After graduation, I couldn't find work.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.04,0:37:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在县上乱逛  看见敲锣打鼓的  喊人报名\N{\rEng}One day in the street, a man was signing people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.04,0:37:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道干啥的  没仔细问  我就报了一个\N{\rEng}I didn't know what for, but I signed up anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.54,0:38:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不就来了\N{\rEng}And I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.05,0:38:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不后悔\N{\rEng}Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.05,0:38:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不后悔\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.55,0:38:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.55,0:38:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢\N{\rEng}I like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.55,0:38:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生还没成家\N{\rEng}Are you married?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.56,0:38:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没呢\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.06,0:38:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没定亲\N{\rEng}Are you engaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.56,0:38:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没呢\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.07,0:38:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别管  让招娣收拾  坐着  歇会儿\N{\rEng}Di will do it. Sit for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.59,0:38:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认得我家的碗吗\N{\rEng}Do you remember this bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.59,0:38:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这青花的\N{\rEng}This design?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.09,0:38:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认得\N{\rEng}No, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.09,0:38:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃没吃公饭\N{\rEng}Did you eat the food brought to the site?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.10,0:38:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.60,0:38:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是瞎了招娣的一片心了\N{\rEng}Looks like Di's hard work was wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.60,0:39:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看都不说  我可都知道  盖学堂  吃公饭\N{\rEng}You know when you were building the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.61,0:39:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是调着样儿做好的\N{\rEng}she made all her best dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.61,0:39:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回回都拿这青花碗送过去\N{\rEng}She always used that bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.11,0:39:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就指盼着先生能吃上一口\N{\rEng}hoping you would choose her dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.61,0:39:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连我都不让动上一筷子\N{\rEng}Even I wasn't allowed to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.12,0:39:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢  吃公饭啊  这碗我还真使过\N{\rEng}I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.62,0:39:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你使过\N{\rEng}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.62,0:39:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说嘛  有点眼熟  使过\N{\rEng}The bowl and your cooking are familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.12,0:39:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碗里的饭你也吃了\N{\rEng}So you ate from it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.63,0:39:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.63,0:39:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说  都吃啥了\N{\rEng}You did? What did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.63,0:39:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃\N{\rEng}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.13,0:39:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说  我头一天送的是葱花油饼\N{\rEng}On the first day, I made onion cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.64,0:39:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  送的是小米饭  葱花炒鸡蛋\N{\rEng}On the second, scrambled eggs and onions on rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.14,0:39:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三天  送的是蘑菇馅蒸饺\N{\rEng}On the third day, mushroom dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.64,0:39:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啦  这么好吃的三顿饭\N{\rEng}What a shame. Three delicious meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.65,0:39:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘑菇馅蒸饺我最爱吃了\N{\rEng}And I love mushroom dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.15,0:39:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你后晌来  我给你做\N{\rEng}I'll make you some this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.35,0:39:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太麻烦了\N{\rEng}That is too much to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.20,0:39:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不麻烦\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.30,0:39:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这刚吃了前晌\N{\rEng}You've hardly finished lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.30,0:39:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就惦着后晌了\N{\rEng}and you're planning the next meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.66,0:39:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招娣  送先生走  先生还忙着呢\N{\rEng}Di, show the teacher out. He must be very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.16,0:39:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  我该走了\N{\rEng}Yes, I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.68,0:40:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你穿那件红衣裳真好看\N{\rEng}That red jacket of yours is pretty on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.18,0:40:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来的头一天我就看见了\N{\rEng}I remember it from the day I arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.18,0:40:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 后晌你一定要来吃饺子    - 唉\N{\rEng}- Don't forget to come back for dumplings.    - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.20,0:40:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说  就别包那饺子了\N{\rEng}You shouldn't make the dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.70,0:40:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为啥不包\N{\rEng}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.20,0:40:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免得后悔\N{\rEng}You may regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.20,0:40:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我悔啥\N{\rEng}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.20,0:40:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悔啥你自己知道\N{\rEng}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.21,0:40:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那先生  好是好\N{\rEng}This teacher is a nice man,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.21,0:40:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟咱不是一路人  这事儿不成\N{\rEng}but he's out of our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.21,0:40:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啥成不成的  不就吃顿饺子吗\N{\rEng}What are you talking about? It's only dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.71,0:40:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别给我装糊涂\N{\rEng}Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.22,0:40:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把话给你撂下\N{\rEng}I'm just being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.72,0:40:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就死了这心吧\N{\rEng}You'd best forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.74,0:41:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去就是不回去\N{\rEng}I will not go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.75,0:41:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别无选择\N{\rEng}You've got no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.85,0:43:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来跟你说一声  我要走了\N{\rEng}I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.35,0:43:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走  走哪儿啊\N{\rEng}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.86,0:43:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回县里面\N{\rEng}Back to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.86,0:43:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥事儿这么急\N{\rEng}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.36,0:43:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没啥事儿\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.36,0:43:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在井台上看到他跟你吵架了\N{\rEng}I saw you argue with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.86,0:43:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他叫你回去的\N{\rEng}Was that what it was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.87,0:43:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁呀  你回去干啥\N{\rEng}Who was he? Why do you have to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.37,0:43:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没啥事儿\N{\rEng}It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.37,0:43:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是有事儿问我  问完就完了呗\N{\rEng}They just want to ask me some questions. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.37,0:43:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那在这儿不能问\N{\rEng}Can't they ask you questions here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.37,0:43:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做不了主\N{\rEng}He says it's not up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.38,0:43:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你还回来吗\N{\rEng}Will you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.38,0:43:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来  我一定回来  学生们等我上课呢\N{\rEng}Of course. I have classes to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.88,0:43:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你啥时候回来\N{\rEng}When will you be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.72,0:43:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最晚  腊月初八我一定回来\N{\rEng}By the 27th at the latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.64,0:43:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腊月初九  学生放假\N{\rEng}On the 28th, the school holiday starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.36,0:43:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得在放假前回来\N{\rEng}I have to be back before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.40,0:43:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进屋吃饺子吧\N{\rEng}Come in and eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.40,0:43:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饺子恐怕吃不了了\N{\rEng}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.90,0:43:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有事儿呢  你和你娘就别等了\N{\rEng}I have things to do before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.91,0:44:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真还有事儿呢  他等着我呢\N{\rEng}I really do. That man is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.41,0:44:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你招呼他一块儿来吃吧\N{\rEng}Tell him to come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.41,0:44:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥要紧事儿也得先吃饭呐\N{\rEng}You have to eat in any case.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.42,0:44:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  我来吃\N{\rEng}Okay, I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.92,0:44:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我等着你\N{\rEng}I'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.92,0:44:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是我给你买的\N{\rEng}This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.93,0:44:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配你那件红衣裳  好看\N{\rEng}To go with your red jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.94,0:44:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我等着你啊\N{\rEng}I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.44,0:44:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.00,0:44:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底咋回事儿啊  这不正上课着吗\N{\rEng}What is going on? No more class?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.50,0:44:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是要让他当个右派\N{\rEng}He's in some political trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.95,0:44:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥派\N{\rEng}Political trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.46,0:44:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也整不明白  反正没啥大事儿\N{\rEng}I don't understand it either. But maybe it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.06,0:44:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定过两天就回来了\N{\rEng}Said he might be back in a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.49,0:45:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生走了\N{\rEng}The teacher's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.50,0:45:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生走了吗\N{\rEng}The teacher's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.50,0:45:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.50,0:45:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他走了\N{\rEng}Just left?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.50,0:45:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚村长他们把他送走\N{\rEng}Just left with the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.27,0:50:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲一连好几天早出晚归\N{\rEng}My mother retraced her steps every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.28,0:50:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她把那几十里山路都跑遍了\N{\rEng}searching back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.28,0:50:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想找到父亲留给她的那支发夹\N{\rEng}She had to find the clip my father had given her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.72,0:52:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修碗  修盆\N{\rEng}Pottery repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.23,0:52:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锔碗的\N{\rEng}Pottery repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.23,0:52:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锔碗的  进来\N{\rEng}Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.82,0:53:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是照钉收钱的\N{\rEng}I charge for the nails I use.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.83,0:53:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这比买一个新碗可贵多了\N{\rEng}This will cost you more than buying a new bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.33,0:53:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该多少钱给多少钱  分文不短你的\N{\rEng}Just tell me how much, and I'll pay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.33,0:53:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是祖上传下来的吗\N{\rEng}Is it a family heirloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.33,0:53:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.34,0:54:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是有人使过\N{\rEng}It belonged to someone special?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.84,0:54:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你说对了  有人使过\N{\rEng}You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.34,0:54:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁使过\N{\rEng}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.34,0:54:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不瞒你说  我这是替闺女锔的\N{\rEng}It's for my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.85,0:54:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使碗的人走了  把闺女的心也带走了\N{\rEng}The man who used it left
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.85,0:54:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这碗锔好了  也给闺女留个念\N{\rEng}and took my daughter's heart with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.86,0:54:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你把它锔得滴水不漏\N{\rEng}I've put it back together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.86,0:54:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保准给你闺女一个好念想\N{\rEng}I hope she'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.37,0:54:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修碗  修盆\N{\rEng}Pottery repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.40,0:55:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娣儿  你干啥呢\N{\rEng}Di, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.90,0:55:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没干啥  我舀口水喝\N{\rEng}Nothing. Just getting a drink of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.45,0:55:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一八得八\N{\rEng}1 times 8 equals 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.96,0:56:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一九得九\N{\rEng}1 times 9 equals 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.46,0:56:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二二得四\N{\rEng}2 times 2 equals 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.96,0:56:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二三得六\N{\rEng}2 times 3 equals 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.97,0:56:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二四得八\N{\rEng}2 times 4 equals 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.47,0:56:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二五一十\N{\rEng}2 times 5 equals 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.47,0:56:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二六一十二\N{\rEng}2 times 6 equals 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.47,0:56:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二七一十四\N{\rEng}2 times 7 equals 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.48,0:56:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二八一十六\N{\rEng}2 times 8 equals 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.48,0:56:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二九一十八\N{\rEng}2 times 9 equals 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.98,0:56:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\rEng}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.96,0:56:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三三得九\N{\rEng}3 times 3 equals 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.99,0:56:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三四一十二\N{\rEng}3 times 4 equals 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.49,0:56:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三五一十五\N{\rEng}3 times 5 equals 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.49,0:56:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三六一十八\N{\rEng}3 times 6 equals 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.00,0:56:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三七二十一\N{\rEng}3 times 7 equals 21.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.00,0:56:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三八二十四\N{\rEng}3 times 8 equals 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.00,0:56:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三九二十七\N{\rEng}3 times 9 equals 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.56,0:57:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲对母亲说过\N{\rEng}My father told my mother
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.56,0:57:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他给学生上课的时候\N{\rEng}when he was teaching the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.56,0:57:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一抬眼就能看见梁上那块红\N{\rEng}he could always look up and see the red banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.07,0:57:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看见那红\N{\rEng}When he saw that banner
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.07,0:57:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就想起母亲穿红棉袄的样子\N{\rEng}it reminded him of Mother and her red jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.57,0:57:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来村长说过好几次\N{\rEng}The mayor kept insisting
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.57,0:57:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要给教室吊个顶棚\N{\rEng}that the ceiling needed proper insulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.58,0:58:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都被父亲谢绝了\N{\rEng}but my father never let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.08,0:58:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们村的这个小学校  几十年来就一直没有顶棚\N{\rEng}That's why the school ceiling was never completed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.12,1:00:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天母亲在教室里一直坐到很晚\N{\rEng}Mother sat in the classroom for hours that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.62,1:00:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教室门开着  被村长看见了\N{\rEng}The door was open, and the mayor saw her there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.13,1:00:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长这才明白了母亲的心思\N{\rEng}He understood what that meant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.63,1:00:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长知道了\N{\rEng}Once he knew,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.63,1:00:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里人很快也都知道了\N{\rEng}the news got around the village, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.13,1:00:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在当年\N{\rEng}Back then, arranged matches were the rule.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.14,1:00:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由恋爱还是一件很新鲜的事儿\N{\rEng}The freedom of falling in love was unfamiliar.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.14,1:00:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲给三合屯开了个头\N{\rEng}This was a first for our village.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.40,1:00:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了父亲答应回来的日子\N{\rEng}On the day my father promised to return...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.90,1:00:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲一大早就站在那条路上等\N{\rEng}my mother was waiting from first light.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.41,1:00:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她记着父亲说过的那句话\N{\rEng}She remembered his promise:
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.91,1:00:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腊月初八一定回来\N{\rEng}that he would return on the 27th.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.41,1:00:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为腊月初九学校就放假了\N{\rEng}School vacation began on the 28th.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.42,1:00:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲得在放假前赶回来\N{\rEng}He had to be back before that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.98,1:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这身寒气  干啥去了  一天不着家\N{\rEng}It's so cold out. Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.48,1:03:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快上炕躺会儿\N{\rEng}Gone all day. Get warm on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.99,1:03:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么烫  娣儿  你病了\N{\rEng}You're burning up!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.53,1:04:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你昨天迎先生去了\N{\rEng}I know you went to wait for the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.03,1:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里的人都说  先生犯了错误  回不来了\N{\rEng}Everyone says he's in trouble and won't be back.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.64,1:04:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就别操这份心了\N{\rEng}You've got to let go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.54,1:04:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到县上找他去\N{\rEng}I'm going to the city to find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.54,1:04:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了  你还病着呢  你上县上咋找\N{\rEng}Are you crazy?! You're ill!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.05,1:04:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娣儿  你回来  回来\N{\rEng}Di! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.09,1:05:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天母亲没走到县城\N{\rEng}My mother didn't make it to the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.09,1:05:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却晕倒在半路上\N{\rEng}She fainted by the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.59,1:05:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有过路人看见  给村里捎了信儿\N{\rEng}Someone saw her, and they got word to the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.60,1:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长和夏大叔他们套上马车  连夜把母亲拉了回来\N{\rEng}The mayor and my uncle brought her home on a cart.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.60,1:05:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得村长后来跟我说过一次\N{\rEng}The mayor said that day,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.20,1:05:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说那天母亲的两手冰凉冰凉的\N{\rEng}my mother's hands were like ice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.90,1:05:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在马车上\N{\rEng}While on the cart,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.11,1:05:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他用皮袄暖了一路\N{\rEng}they wrapped her in a heavy blanket,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.11,1:05:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都没暖过来\N{\rEng}but they couldn't get her hands warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.12,1:05:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  冻着了\N{\rEng}I don't think it's too serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.12,1:05:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虚火上升  气血淤滞  歇两天就好了\N{\rEng}It's a bad chill, but she is strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.63,1:05:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长  你说说  这先生到底还能不能回来\N{\rEng}Mayor, is the teacher coming back?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.14,1:05:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这城里人的事儿  我也整不清楚\N{\rEng}I don't know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.64,1:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照理说  他也该早回来了\N{\rEng}He should have been back by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.64,1:06:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有谁方便啊  就给先生捎个信\N{\rEng}Maybe someone can write to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.65,1:06:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不回来  招娣咋办  我也拦不住她呀\N{\rEng}I don't know how to help her...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.15,1:06:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让先生回来呀  看上她一眼也好啊\N{\rEng}if he doesn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.58,1:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天来了\N{\rEng}"Spring is here."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.03,1:06:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天来了\N{\rEng}"Spring is here."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.54,1:06:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春风吹化了冰雪\N{\rEng}"It melts the snow."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.52,1:06:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春风吹化了冰雪\N{\rEng}"It melts the snow."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.01,1:06:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹绿了草地\N{\rEng}"The grass turns green."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.51,1:06:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹绿了草地\N{\rEng}"The grass turns green."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.01,1:06:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,农民在种庄稼\N{\rEng}"The farmers sow."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.52,1:06:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,农民在种庄稼\N{\rEng}"The farmers sow."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.02,1:06:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛在耕田\N{\rEng}"The ox plow the field."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.52,1:06:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛在耕田\N{\rEng}"The ox plow the field."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.52,1:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大雁回来了\N{\rEng}"The wild geese return."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.52,1:06:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大雁回来了\N{\rEng}"The wild geese return."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.03,1:06:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙结束了冬眠\N{\rEng}"The frogs begin to hop."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.53,1:06:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙结束了冬眠\N{\rEng}"The frogs begin to hop."
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.03,1:06:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娣儿  你醒了\N{\rEng}Di, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.53,1:07:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都睡了两天了\N{\rEng}You've been sleeping for two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.53,1:07:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不知道呢\N{\rEng}Di, the teacher is back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.23,1:07:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生回来了\N{\rEng}The teacher is back.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.04,1:07:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生昨晚就回来了\N{\rEng}He came back yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.04,1:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一回来就上咱们家来了\N{\rEng}He came straight here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.04,1:07:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这儿守了你半宿\N{\rEng}He sat with you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.55,1:07:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娣儿  这下可好了  先生回来了\N{\rEng}Isn't it good news?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.05,1:07:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他这是为你回来的呀\N{\rEng}He came back for you.
