Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.63,1:08:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骆先生\N{\rEng}Mr. Luo!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.63,1:08:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骆先生  招娣来看你了\N{\rEng}Mr. Luo, Di is here to see you!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.64,1:08:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  先生\N{\rEng}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.65,1:08:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招娣来了\N{\rEng}Di is here!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.18,1:08:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天黑前  刚刚回来的父亲就又被叫走了\N{\rEng}That evening, my father had to leave again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.15,1:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是偷着跑回来的\N{\rEng}When he heard about my mother, he left the city...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.15,1:08:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是听说了母亲的情况后\N{\rEng}without permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.15,1:09:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在忍不住\N{\rEng}He couldn't stand it any longer,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.15,1:09:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就私自跑回来了\N{\rEng}so he sneaked back.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.66,1:09:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于父亲的这次行为\N{\rEng}For this disobedience,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.16,1:09:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使他和母亲最后见面的日子又推迟了好几年\N{\rEng}my parents were kept apart for another two years.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.67,1:09:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来  我听乡亲们说\N{\rEng}Someone told me,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.17,1:09:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当父亲真正和母亲相聚的那一天到来时\N{\rEng}that on the day my father finally returned,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.17,1:09:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲又特意穿上了那件\N{\rEng}my mother put on her red jacket,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.67,1:09:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲喜爱的红棉袄\N{\rEng}my father's favorite,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.18,1:09:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在路边等着父亲\N{\rEng}and stood by the road to wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.68,1:09:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起  父亲就再没离开过母亲一步\N{\rEng}From that day on, my father never left my mother again.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.20,1:09:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是父亲和母亲的故事\N{\rEng}This is the story of my father and my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.20,1:09:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们相识  相爱的过程  都和这条路有关\N{\rEng}This road is part of their love story...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.21,1:09:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们村通往县城的一条普通的山路\N{\rEng}this road that leads from the city to our village.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.71,1:10:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许就因为母亲曾经那么殷切\N{\rEng}Maybe because of the hope it held for her
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.72,1:10:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么长久地在这条路上等待过父亲\N{\rEng}as she waited for my father to return,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.72,1:10:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她还想陪着父亲  再从这条路上走回来\N{\rEng}she wants to walk this way with him one last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.73,1:10:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长\N{\rEng}Mr. Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.23,1:10:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长\N{\rEng}Mr. Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.73,1:10:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁呀\N{\rEng}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.73,1:10:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  生子\N{\rEng}It's me, Yusheng.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.74,1:10:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 生子  有事儿吗    - 有事儿\N{\rEng}- You need to see me?    - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.24,1:10:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事儿快进屋说  来  天挺冷的\N{\rEng}Come in, come in. It's cold out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.74,1:10:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事儿啊\N{\rEng}How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.25,1:10:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈的心思啊  我想明白了\N{\rEng}I've thought it through.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.75,1:10:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们还是抬吧\N{\rEng}I want to do as my mother wishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.25,1:10:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要抬\N{\rEng}To carry him back?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.25,1:10:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是咱们村还有点困难\N{\rEng}It's still a problem, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.76,1:10:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是人手不够吗\N{\rEng}The problem is not enough men, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.76,1:10:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这样行不行  村长\N{\rEng}How about this:
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.26,1:10:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们到邻村雇点人来\N{\rEng}We'll hire men from the next village.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.76,1:10:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雇人  邻村倒是好雇\N{\rEng}That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.27,1:10:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就这钱\N{\rEng}But how do we pay them?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.27,1:10:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那没关系  您帮我算算得多少人\N{\rEng}Just tell me how many men we need.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.27,1:11:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人嘛  要是近点  有十几多个人就够\N{\rEng}For a short distance, only 10,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.28,1:11:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为咱们这儿离县城太远\N{\rEng}but this is a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.28,1:11:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个你必须得十六个人的杠子\N{\rEng}I think we need about 16.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.78,1:11:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得两班  两班就得三十二个\N{\rEng}We will need two shifts. That's 32 men.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.79,1:11:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三十二个呢  再有几个闲人  拿凳子放在路中\N{\rEng}And we'll need others to carry chairs,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.10,1:11:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的人累了  可以搁上歇歇\N{\rEng}so people can rest along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.29,1:11:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这总共得个三十五六个人吧\N{\rEng}That comes to about 35, 36 men.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.30,1:11:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一个人得多少钱呢\N{\rEng}How much per person?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.80,1:11:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人  现在咱就给他一百块钱\N{\rEng}One hundred yuan each should do.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.30,1:11:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以了\N{\rEng}That will do.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.81,1:11:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三十五六个人\N{\rEng}Thirty-five, 36 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.31,1:11:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你给算算总共得多少钱\N{\rEng}How much in total?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.31,1:11:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人嘛  三十五六个人  三千五六百块钱\N{\rEng}That's 3500 or 3600 yuan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.81,1:11:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下来呀  有抽烟的  咱们还要给他买点烟\N{\rEng}We need to buy cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.82,1:11:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有喝酒的  这酒我也得买点  因为天太冷\N{\rEng}And wine too, gotta ward off the cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.82,1:11:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要有点什么事儿  都得用点钱\N{\rEng}We'll also want a little extra for emergency use.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.83,1:11:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能有四千多块钱  就差不多了\N{\rEng}Altogether, around 4000 yuan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.34,1:12:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长  这是五千块钱  够不够\N{\rEng}Here's 5000 yuan. Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.34,1:12:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足够了  用不了\N{\rEng}It's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.39,1:13:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老嫂子  去看看骆先生吧\N{\rEng}Mrs. Luo, come and see Mr. Luo.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.90,1:13:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看的时候可别哭\N{\rEng}Please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.90,1:13:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让眼泪掉在骆先生身上  不好的\N{\rEng}Don't let tears fall on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.91,1:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骆先生  咱们现在回村了  要走好\N{\rEng}Mr. Luo, we are going back to the village.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.92,1:13:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天抬棺来了一百多个人\N{\rEng}That day over 100 people came to the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.92,1:13:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听村长说  他们都是父亲的学生\N{\rEng}The mayor told me they were my father's students.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.42,1:13:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道了这件事情  就都赶来了\N{\rEng}They heard about his death, and they all came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.43,1:13:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人都是从外地赶回来的\N{\rEng}Many came from other towns.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.93,1:13:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有从市里坐着小车来的\N{\rEng}Some drove from the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.93,1:13:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长说  最远的有从广州赶过来的\N{\rEng}The mayor said some came from as far as Guangzhou.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.44,1:13:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有几个人被风雪误在了半路上\N{\rEng}Some tried, but didn't make it in time,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.44,1:13:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有来得及\N{\rEng}because of the snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.94,1:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来得人大部分我都不认识\N{\rEng}I didn't recognize many of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.45,1:13:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的人比我大得多\N{\rEng}Many were older than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.95,1:13:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他们都是父亲哪一年的学生\N{\rEng}I don't know when my father taught them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.95,1:14:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道该怎样称呼他们\N{\rEng}I didn't know how to address them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.96,1:14:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长说\N{\rEng}Anyway, as the mayor said,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.46,1:14:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是骆先生的学生嘛\N{\rEng}they are all my father's students.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.96,1:14:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生子  这些钱还给你吧\N{\rEng}Take this money back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.46,1:14:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咋能都不要呢  不是说好了的吗\N{\rEng}Why? Didn't you pay the men?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.97,1:14:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来的人都不要  就连拿钱雇的人也不要\N{\rEng}They won't take it, not even the ones we hired.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.47,1:14:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一分钱也不要\N{\rEng}No one wants the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.47,1:14:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是收起来吧\N{\rEng}Take it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.13,1:17:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按着母亲的意思\N{\rEng}At my mother's request,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.64,1:17:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲就安葬在前井旁边\N{\rEng}my father was buried next to the old well.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.14,1:17:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里有了自来水  井就荒了\N{\rEng}The village has running water now, so no one needs a well.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.64,1:17:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就没人再挑水了\N{\rEng}No one draws water from it now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.15,1:17:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲说  在这儿\N{\rEng}My mother says from this hill,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.15,1:17:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲可以天天看见学校\N{\rEng}my father can look down on the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.15,1:17:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲还说  将来她也要跟父亲埋在一起\N{\rEng}She asks to be buried next to him when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.70,1:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,办完父亲的后事\N{\rEng}After my father's funeral,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.67,1:17:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长特意来说起了盖学校的事儿\N{\rEng}the mayor came to talk about rebuilding the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.17,1:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说县里拨了款\N{\rEng}The city has granted funds,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.78,1:17:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里家家户户也都捐了钱\N{\rEng}and the village families have donated money.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.68,1:17:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说乡亲们无论如何也要完成父亲的心愿\N{\rEng}He says we must fulfill my father's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.48,1:17:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生子  你带回来的钱呢  给妈吧\N{\rEng}Your money, give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.69,1:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长  你看  这些钱都是我这几十年积攒的\N{\rEng}Mayor, we've saved over the years.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.20,1:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把它收起来盖学校吧\N{\rEng}Take it to rebuild the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.70,1:18:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这咋好意思呢  你说  长余不在了\N{\rEng}I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.00,1:18:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这钱你一定得收下\N{\rEng}With my husband gone, you have to take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.21,1:18:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好  那我把这些钱先拿上\N{\rEng}All right, I'll take it then.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.22,1:18:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们村  你们母子俩算第一份\N{\rEng}You are the first, but surely not the last, to help.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.71,1:18:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我就要走了\N{\rEng}I am leaving tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.22,1:18:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲让我陪她再去一趟学校\N{\rEng}Mother has asked me to go to the schoolhouse one last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.22,1:18:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲说  等下次我再回来时\N{\rEng}My mother says the next time I come back,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.22,1:18:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这所小学校就看不到了\N{\rEng}the school we know will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.73,1:18:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生子  你看这学校都几十年了\N{\rEng}Your father helped build this school.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.23,1:18:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸就在这学校教书\N{\rEng}He taught here so many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.24,1:18:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里比在家待得时间还长\N{\rEng}Spent as much time here as at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.24,1:18:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长余  你都听到了吗\N{\rEng}Changyu, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.25,1:18:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长说了  要盖新学校\N{\rEng}The mayor will rebuild the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.25,1:19:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按你的心愿去盖  盖一个高大  漂漂亮亮的\N{\rEng}They'll build a tall
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.76,1:19:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个好学校\N{\rEng}and wonderful school...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.26,1:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了完成你的心愿  按你的意思去盖\N{\rEng}just as you wished.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.27,1:19:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明年开春就动工了\N{\rEng}They will start building next spring.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.27,1:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这回你放心了吧\N{\rEng}You won't have to worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.78,1:19:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新学校盖好了\N{\rEng}When the school is completed,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.78,1:19:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲手织一块红挂上去\N{\rEng}I will hang a lucky red banner there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.29,1:19:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就放心吧\N{\rEng}You can rest easy now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.30,1:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看你爸  实心实意\N{\rEng}You know, your father was a sincere man.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.76,1:19:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整天跟我说  想叫你教书\N{\rEng}He always wanted you to become a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.76,1:20:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接他的班\N{\rEng}to take over for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.76,1:20:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你送到师范学校念了\N{\rEng}You went to the teachers' college,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.77,1:20:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天书你也没教上\N{\rEng}but you never taught a day of class.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.77,1:20:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕你上一天课  教一天书\N{\rEng}If you could teach for one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.78,1:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是你爸爸这一片心都没有实现了\N{\rEng}I think it would make him happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.28,1:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就干别的工作去了\N{\rEng}Then you can go back to your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.29,1:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  学校连上课的人都没有了\N{\rEng}Look, there's no teacher now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.30,1:20:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听不到孩子们念书的声音了\N{\rEng}No sound of children reciting their lessons.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.30,1:20:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听村长说  过两天县上可能还会派个新老师来\N{\rEng}The mayor said a new teacher was on the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.31,1:20:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新老师来\N{\rEng}Not many teachers,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.31,1:20:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再上课也没有你爸爸声音好听啊  特别的响亮\N{\rEng}would sound as good as your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.32,1:20:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四十多年我都没听够\N{\rEng}After 40 years, I still love that voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.32,1:21:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好听呀  你爸读书\N{\rEng}I can still hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.83,1:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈  我考虑好了\N{\rEng}Mother, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.33,1:21:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次你跟我回城里  咱们一块儿住\N{\rEng}Why don't you come to the city with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.34,1:21:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去\N{\rEng}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.84,1:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有你爸在这儿  哪儿我也不去\N{\rEng}I won't leave your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.34,1:21:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你自己留在这儿  让我咋放心呢\N{\rEng}How can I leave you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.35,1:21:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别为我担心\N{\rEng}Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.35,1:21:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己会照顾我自己的\N{\rEng}I can take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.85,1:21:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在城里工作都好吧\N{\rEng}Are you doing all right in the city?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.36,1:21:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  妈\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.36,1:21:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别好  你放心吧\N{\rEng}Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.86,1:21:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有女朋友吗\N{\rEng}Do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.86,1:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再说吧\N{\rEng}Let's not talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.87,1:21:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  你都那么大岁数了\N{\rEng}You're not young anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.37,1:21:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别挑剔了啊\N{\rEng}Don't be so picky.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.37,1:21:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听妈告诉你\N{\rEng}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.37,1:21:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有合适的  自己找一个\N{\rEng}Find yourself a nice girl
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.38,1:21:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找一个领回来  让妈看看\N{\rEng}and bring her home to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.39,1:22:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  你爸不在了\N{\rEng}Your father's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.89,1:22:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸呀  就为你这事担心\N{\rEng}He used to worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.90,1:22:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儿女大了  拴不住了\N{\rEng}Our children must leave home.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.40,1:22:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离爹娘远了  就看不到了\N{\rEng}We can't keep you here forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.91,1:22:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做父母的\N{\rEng}As parents...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.92,1:22:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儿女出了门  父母都担心呐  你看\N{\rEng}we let you go, but we never stopped worrying.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.92,1:22:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爸  一直\N{\rEng}Your father...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.43,1:22:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都挂念你  记着你\N{\rEng}...missed you so.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.94,1:22:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别哭了  妈    - 你看他\N{\rEng}- Please don't cry.    - Your father...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.07,1:22:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老哭老哭  你看你这身体都坏了\N{\rEng}Mother, please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.44,1:23:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看他去了  把咱们母子留下  孤孤单单的\N{\rEng}With your father gone, it's hard not to feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.95,1:23:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEng}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.45,1:23:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀\N{\rEng}You...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.96,1:23:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在外面好好工作啊\N{\rEng}...must work hard and make a good life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.50,1:24:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能写会算  是件好事  念\N{\rEng}"One must learn to read and write."
