Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.05,1:24:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一大早就让村长把学生们集合起来\N{\rEng}I gathered the students early that morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.55,1:24:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说我要给学生们上一节课\N{\rEng}I told them I would teach them for one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.56,1:24:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村长问我为什么\N{\rEng}The mayor asked me why.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.56,1:25:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说我是为了母亲  也为了父亲\N{\rEng}I said it was for my mother and for my father too.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.56,1:25:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就站在父亲常站的那个地方\N{\rEng}I stood in my father's place,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.57,1:25:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲在这儿站了一辈子\N{\rEng}where he stood for so many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.57,1:25:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想  此时此刻  父亲一定能听见\N{\rEng}I felt sure he could hear my voice,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.07,1:25:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和孩子们念书的声音吧\N{\rEng}and those of the students.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.58,1:25:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我念的就是当年父亲在开学第一天念的那篇课文\N{\rEng}The book I am using is the same one he used that first day.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.08,1:25:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实这不是正式的课文\N{\rEng}It is not a textbook.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.58,1:25:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是父亲自己编的一段识字歌儿\N{\rEng}It is a book he wrote himself.
